---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact RecastCalc"
  description="Contact RecastCalc with corrections, lender data updates, or partnership inquiries."
>
  <article class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 py-16 prose-recast">
    <h1 class="text-display-1 font-display font-semibold mb-8">Contact</h1>

    <p class="text-lg">
      Send all inquiries to <strong>hello@recastcalc.com</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2>What we respond to fast (within 48 hours)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Math errors or inconsistencies in calculator results</li>
      <li>Out-of-date lender policy data (especially recast fees, minimum lump sums, eligibility changes)</li>
      <li>Press inquiries from journalists working on mortgage, housing, or personal finance stories — we share methodology, source data, and original research</li>
      <li>Requests to use our calculators or data with attribution</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we don't respond to</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Personalized financial advice requests — we are not licensed to provide this</li>
      <li>Loan origination or refinance questions — please contact a licensed lender</li>
      <li>Cold sales pitches or "guest post" SEO inquiries</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Press &amp; data</h2>
    <p>
      Journalists working on mortgage, housing, or personal finance topics: we maintain original
      research datasets including our quarterly survey of lender recast policies. Available on
      request with attribution.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
